WITH MovieDetails AS (
    SELECT 
        t.id AS movie_id, 
        t.title, 
        t.production_year,
        COUNT(DISTINCT ci.person_id) AS actor_count,
        STRING_AGG(DISTINCT a.name, ', ') AS actor_names
    FROM 
        aka_title t
    LEFT JOIN 
        complete_cast cc ON t.id = cc.movie_id
    LEFT JOIN 
        cast_info ci ON cc.subject_id = ci.id
    LEFT JOIN 
        aka_name a ON ci.person_id = a.person_id
    WHERE 
        t.production_year >= 2000
    GROUP BY 
        t.id, t.title, t.production_year
),

KeywordStats AS (
    SELECT 
        mk.movie_id,
        COUNT(mk.keyword_id) AS keyword_count
    FROM 
        movie_keyword mk
    GROUP BY 
        mk.movie_id
),

FinalStats AS (
    SELECT 
        md.movie_id,
        md.title,
        md.production_year,
        md.actor_count,
        ks.keyword_count,
        CASE 
            WHEN md.actor_count IS NULL THEN 0 
            ELSE md.actor_count 
        END AS actor_count_safe,
        CASE 
            WHEN ks.keyword_count IS NULL THEN 0 
            ELSE ks.keyword_count 
        END AS keyword_count_safe
    FROM 
        MovieDetails md
    LEFT JOIN 
        KeywordStats ks ON md.movie_id = ks.movie_id
)

SELECT 
    fs.movie_id, 
    fs.title, 
    fs.production_year,
    fs.actor_count_safe,
    fs.keyword_count_safe,
    COALESCE(fs.actor_count_safe - fs.keyword_count_safe, 0) AS actor_keyword_diff
FROM 
    FinalStats fs
ORDER BY 
    fs.production_year DESC, 
    fs.actor_count_safe DESC

SELECT COALESCE("movie_id", "movie_id") AS "MOVIE_ID"
FROM "movie_keyword"

SELECT COALESCE("t4"."MOVIE_ID", "t4"."MOVIE_ID") AS "MOVIE_ID", "t4"."TITLE", "t4"."PRODUCTION_YEAR", "t4"."ACTOR_COUNT" AS "ACTOR_COUNT_SAFE", CASE WHEN "t5"."KEYWORD_COUNT" IS NULL THEN 0 ELSE "t5"."KEYWORD_COUNT" END AS "KEYWORD_COUNT_SAFE", CASE WHEN CASE WHEN "t5"."KEYWORD_COUNT" IS NULL THEN 0 ELSE "t5"."KEYWORD_COUNT" END IS NOT NULL THEN CAST("t4"."ACTOR_COUNT" - CASE WHEN "t5"."KEYWORD_COUNT" IS NULL THEN 0 ELSE "t5"."KEYWORD_COUNT" END AS BIGINT) ELSE 0 END AS "ACTOR_KEYWORD_DIFF"
FROM (SELECT MIN("aka_title"."id") AS "MOVIE_ID", "aka_title"."title" AS "TITLE", "aka_title"."production_year" AS "PRODUCTION_YEAR", COUNT(DISTINCT "cast_info"."person_id") AS "ACTOR_COUNT", LISTAGG(DISTINCT "aka_name"."name", ', ') AS "ACTOR_NAMES"
FROM "aka_title"
LEFT JOIN "complete_cast" ON "aka_title"."id" = "complete_cast"."movie_id"
LEFT JOIN "cast_info" ON "complete_cast"."subject_id" = "cast_info"."id"
LEFT JOIN "aka_name" ON "cast_info"."person_id" = "aka_name"."person_id"
WHERE "aka_title"."production_year" >= 2000
GROUP BY "aka_title"."id", "aka_title"."title", "aka_title"."production_year") AS "t4"
LEFT JOIN (SELECT "MOVIE_ID", COUNT(*) AS "KEYWORD_COUNT"
FROM "s1"
GROUP BY "MOVIE_ID") AS "t5" ON "t4"."MOVIE_ID" = "t5"."MOVIE_ID"
ORDER BY "t4"."PRODUCTION_YEAR" DESC NULLS FIRST, "t4"."ACTOR_COUNT" DESC NULLS FIRST
